’Ů@e64b70f0fe5390278c655a4c3656ae01be21c841944e2e34db74b78bfcc4133aÚUTitle: title: random chars
Path: Examples
Content:
Generate a string with 25 random chars.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> random chars


```
Generate random chars with specified length.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> random chars --length 20


```
Generate one kilobyte of random chars.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> random chars --length 1kb


```
